dom:
<input class="sessioncamhidetext form-control " data-bind="
				value: field,
				valueupdate: ['afterkeydown', 'input'],
				hasfocus: field.isfocus,
				disable: $data.disabled,
				inlinevalidation: {
					position: '' || 'bottom',
					id: 'customernumbervalidation',
					isfeedbackvisible: ko.computed(function() { return !field.trackedisvalid() }),
					isvalid: false,
					isnotvalid: ko.computed(function() { return !field.trackedisvalid() }),
					feedback: field.error
				}
			" data-track-id="" id="customernumber" maxlength="10" name="customernumber" placeholder="" type="text" value=""/>
feature: your pre approved customer number your pre approved customer number customernumber text customernumber 10
